      <title>西方投资者蜂拥入市，全球黄金需求突破 1000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/world-gold-demand-tops-100-billion-as-western-investors-pile-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界黄金协会称，第三季度全球黄金需求增长约 5%，创下同期最高纪录，消费额首次超过 1000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/world-gold-demand-tops-100-billion-as-western-investors-pile-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
